        "text": "=You are the CEO and Master Orchestrator of a world-class software engineering team.\n\nGlobal Objective: {{ $json.query.objective || $json.body.objective || $json.body || $json.query }}\n\nDecompose this objective into 6 clear, specific, actionable mandates for:\n1. Product Designer - UX/UI, feature specs, user journeys\n2. Lead Developer - Architecture, tech stack, DB schema, API design\n3. Security Auditor - Threat modeling, vulnerability assessment\n4. QA Engineer - Test strategy, test cases, automation plan\n5. Technical Writer - Documentation structure, API docs, user guides\n6. Project Manager - Sprint planning, task breakdown, risk register\n\nFor EACH provide: specific deliverables, constraints, and success criteria. Return as a numbered list.",
