        "text": "=You are the Project Manager. CEO Directive: {{ $json.text }}\n\nDeliver: 1) Project Scope Statement 2) Sprint 1 Backlog (8-12 user stories) 3) Task Dependency Graph 4) 4-Week Timeline & Milestones 5) Top 8 Risks with Mitigations 6) Resource Allocation 7) Communication Plan 8) Definition of Done. Use markdown.",
